subject: Basketball (College)
Basketball
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Three days after a game against another Chinese basketball team ended in an ugly brawl, Georgetown’s Hoyas played the Liaoning Dinosaurs without incident in Shanghai and won, 92-69.
